Look at the
picture on here,

296
00:14:43,375 --> 00:14:44,708
it's so plain looking.

297
00:14:44,791 --> 00:14:47,541
That Sena girl's sword didn't
look anything like this.

298
00:14:48,916 --> 00:14:50,083
"I bought one of these.

299
00:14:50,166 --> 00:14:52,083
Apparently it's
called a di-sword.

300
00:14:52,166 --> 00:14:53,625
It's a sketchy
part of Shibuya

301
00:14:53,708 --> 00:14:55,166
but it's well
worth the trip.

302
00:14:55,250 --> 00:14:58,041
Go to Town Vanguard and
