00:14:58,125 --> 00:15:00,000
"Wow, you can buy a di-sword.

304
00:15:00,083 --> 00:15:01,625
Hey, I don't think that
Town Vanguard place

305
00:15:01,708 --> 00:15:03,458
is too far from here...

306
00:15:03,541 --> 00:15:05,291
If you really need it,
you should go buy one!

307
