Did you buy this, too?

344
00:17:11,833 --> 00:17:13,416
It came with the sword.

345
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:14,458
It's cool...

346
00:17:14,541 --> 00:17:15,875
Hey, let me
have this, okay?

347
00:17:15,958 --> 00:17:17,750
-Huh?
-Why not...?

348
00:17:17,833 --> 00:17:19,541
Would it kill you to
give me something...?

349
00:17:19,625 --> 00:17:20,708
Come on, give
me a present!

350
00:17:20,791 --> 00:17:22,416
-Oh fine.
-Really...? ...

351
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:24,625
Yay!

352
00:17:24,708 --> 00:17:26,208
What do you
think, Taku...?

353
00:17:26,291 --> 00:17:27,750
How's it look?

354
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:30,083
I really like this, so no matter
what you say, it's mine...!

355
00:17:30,166 --> 00:17:32,250
As a matter of fact, this
might be the first time

356
00:17:32,333 --> 00:17:34,791
you've given me a present,
so how about that? !

357
00:17:34,875 --> 00:17:36,291
You're finished with your
business here, right...?

358
00:17:36,375 --> 00:17:37,500
Go home.

359
00:17:37,583 --> 00:17:39,458
I really don't appreciate
your attitude...

360
00:17:39,541 --> 00:17:41,250
Besides, what
about the oranges...?

361
