Make tea at home.

363
00:17:48,458 --> 00:17:49,583
Suit yourself! . . . !

364
00:17:49,666 --> 00:17:51,041
If I'm in the way,
then I'll leave!

365
00:17:52,791 --> 00:17:54,791
I hate your guts...! I
hope you choke to death

366
00:17:54,875 --> 00:17:56,916
