you stupid jerk!

367
00:17:59,791 --> 00:18:00,916
You deserved that!

368
00:18:04,125 --> 00:18:05,958
It's broken, my only hope!

369
00:18:10,666 --> 00:18:12,000
Yo... Taku...

370
00:18:12,083 --> 00:18:14,458
What's up, takin' a break
from otaku life...?

371
00:18:14,541 --> 00:18:16,000
Hey, what's wrong...?

372
00:18:16,083 --> 00:18:17,833
You in power
nap mode already?

373
00:18:17,916 --> 00:18:19,250
Leave him alone!

374
00:18:19,333 --> 00:18:20,958
The devil girl.

375
00:18:21,041 --> 00:18:22,708
Taku needs some
peace and quiet...

376
