whisper something...

402
00:19:36,625 --> 00:19:38,166
But I didn't hear
what though...

403
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:40,166
Do you two know each
other from somewhere?

404
00:19:41,875 --> 00:19:43,875
I always assumed you weren't
interested in real women,

405
00:19:43,958 --> 00:19:45,291
