make me her boyfriend?

412
00:20:00,916 --> 00:20:02,375
I'll stop
talking to her...

413
00:20:02,458 --> 00:20:03,875
If I don't, I'm
gonna go insane!

414
00:20:05,541 --> 00:20:07,458
Wait... Taku!

415
00:20:14,625 --> 00:20:15,750
I've had enough...

416
00:20:15,833 --> 00:20:17,625
