491
00:24:25,583 --> 00:24:26,916
I'm really sorry.

492
00:24:29,583 --> 00:24:31,916
But wow, you scared
me back there...!

493
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:33,541
I saw you lying
down on the ground

494
00:24:33,625 --> 00:24:35,333
